&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/AFR-SOUTH-AFRICA-THE-GREENHOUSE-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;alignnone size-full wp-image-7303&quot; src=&quot;http://dinersclubofferstool.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/04/AFR-SOUTH-AFRICA-THE-GREENHOUSE-OFFER-LOGO.jpg&quot; alt=&quot;AFR- SOUTH AFRICA- THE GREENHOUSE- OFFER-LOGO&quot; width=&quot;75&quot; height=&quot;75&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;
&lt;/a&gt;The Greenhouse is located in the town of Stellenboch on the wine region outskirts of Cape Town. Situated at the elegantly cozy Cellars-Hohenort Hotel, the understatedly elegant dining room looks onto lush gardens through large windows, becoming an integral part of the dining experience. The cuisine takes inspiration from the diverse cultures, flavors and local produce of South Africa.&nbsp; Chef Peter Tempelhoff, a Relais &amp;amp; Ch&acirc;teaux Grand Chef, and his team work magic, earning a place on the Worlds 50 Best Academy Global Selection list. The expansive wine list focuses on local South African vintners with some international selections as well. Attire is chic casual.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Bookings: Contact The Greenhouse by phone at +27-21-794-2137 or by email at &lt;a href=&quot;mailto:greenhouseres@cellars-hohenort.co.za&quot;&gt;greenhouseres@cellars-hohenort.co.za&lt;/a&gt;&nbsp;to make your reservation.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Mention Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection to receive your special benefit&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide your name, date you would like to dine, number of guests, preferred time, cell phone or local (hotel) phone number and email address&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Greenhouse requires a credit card at the time of booking to hold your reservation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Cancellation Policy: If not cancelled 17h00 one day prior to the dining date or in the event of a no show, a fee in the amount of R600.00 per person will be charged to your credit card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Reconfirmation Policy: The Greenhouse will reconfirm your dinner reservation by phone or email 24 hours prior to your dining date to reconfirm. Provide a reminder that this is a Diners Club International Privileges Dining Collection reservation. If not reconfirmed, your reservation may be given away if need arises.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;TERMS &amp;amp; CONDITIONS&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Follow booking instructions to ensure receiving your Privileges Dining Collection amenity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Based on Availability at the time of booking&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The Greenhouse has tasting menus only. Wine &amp;amp; Beverage pairing at an additional cost&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Your Privileges Dining Collection benefit may not be combined with other offers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fulfillment of the offer is the sole responsibility of the participating&nbsp;Diners Club International&nbsp;Restaurant Merchant&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Restaurant participation and benefits are subject to change or cancellation without notice&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Payment must be made with your Diners Club card&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;

